          <p class="text-amber-800/70 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-base">
            Montaż listew, drobne naprawy i wszystkie prace wykończeniowe. Kompleksowe podejście do detali w Twoim wnętrzu.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-amber-700 font-medium">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-3 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
